channel.title: Fishing not working
channel.description:
I am trying to get my server up and running and I have come across a big problem. The fishing doesn't work.
This source is based off of Torva-Pkz, and the name of it is Impozzes or something like that.
When I go to click on the ripples in the water nothing happens. I tried using the net on the ripples and nothing happened again. Another thing is there are like 20 ripples and they are piling on top of each other.
I have searched through where I think the problem might be, but I have no idea what to look for. If anyone could help me out I would really appreciate it.
